title: S3 E9: Christmas Joy
description:
This week, Maggie & Tim talk about Season 3 Episode 9, the one where a little girl gets Shawn and Gus to help save Santa and the Guster family reveal a bit too many secrets...

Disclaimer: In this episode we talk about Santa and all that comes with that so prepare your kids accordingly.
